Prof Fils Fotso is the most caring prof I've had so far. He is very rigorous, but this is a quality needed to succeed in this course. He acknowledges when he makes a mistake. The notes are clear, midterms are often a copy-paste from the DGDs. I would definitely take him again.

Dr Fotso is an amazing professor. I was very surprised of the bad reviews. He actually cares about his students succeeding. only thing he needs improvement on is his technology when he writes extra notes
